<fn fn-type="other" id="bio1-1464884911421067">
<p>David M. Ryfe is an Associate Professor in the Reynolds School of Journalism, University of Nevada, Reno. He has written in the areas of presidential communication, deliberative practice, and the history and sociology of journalism. His current project is an ethnographic study of American newspapers.</p>
